{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778432193889,"sessionID":"ses_1ed2e5abdffeV49GJQcR5nFb98","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_DiYLiGyV45scGOJoM97efntF","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json","offset":1,"limit":2000},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"Please provide as much information as you can: \\n\\n* **Suggested term label:**\\n@genegodbold Put new terms in here\\n\\n* **Definition (free text)**\\n\\n\\n* **Reference, in format PMID:#######**\\n(REQUIRED)\\n\\n* **Gene product name and ID to be annotated to this term**\\n\\n\\n* **Parent term(s)**\\n\\n\\n* **Children terms (if applicable)** Should any existing terms that should be moved underneath this new proposed term?\\n\\n\\n* **Synonyms (please specify, EXACT, BROAD, NARROW or RELATED)**\\n\\n* **Cross-references**\\n* For enzymes, please provide RHEA and/or EC numbers. \\n* Can also provide MetaCyc, KEGG, Wikipedia, and other links.\\n\\n* **Any other information**\\n\",\n3:   \"comments\": [],\n4:   \"title\": \"NTR: [symbiont-mediated suppression of platelet aggregation]\",\n5:   \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31936\"\n6: }\n\n(End of file - total 6 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"body\": \"Please provide as much information as you can: \\n\\n* **Suggested term label:**\\n@genegodbold Put new terms in here\\n\\n* **Definition (free text)**\\n\\n\\n* **Reference, in format PMID:#######**\\n(REQUIRED)\\n\\n* **Gene product name and ID to be annotated to this term**\\n\\n\\n* **Parent term(s)**\\n\\n\\n* **Children terms (if applicable)** Should any existing terms that should be moved underneath this new proposed term?\\n\\n\\n* **Synonyms (please specify, EXACT, BROAD, NARROW or RELATED)**\\n\\n* **Cross-references**\\n* For enzymes, please provide RHEA and/or EC numbers. \\n* Can also provide MetaCyc, KEGG, Wikipedia, and other links.\\n\\n* **Any other information**\\n\",\n  \"comments\": [],\n  \"title\": \"NTR: [symbiont-mediated suppression of platelet aggregation]\",\n  \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31936\"\n}","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"__issue_context__.json","time":{"start":1778432193865,"end":1778432193887}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0762746a731f6394016a00b8c1a89c819489b2348de406d8bd"}},"id":"prt_e12d1b4a4001kx80YMbfRtvpy8","sessionID":"ses_1ed2e5abdffeV49GJQcR5nFb98","messageID":"msg_e12d1a60d001S34KkqgrEZKY57"}}
